  "text": "Here is our understanding of your business and your needs. Equalize is trusted by food safety leaders. And you've built this trust over 25 years and in different countries. We understand what is at stake. We understand the nature of the food safety industry and the global brands that you service. As a market leader and a thought leader in this space, we are excited to engage with you in building your vision for a digital platform. We are excited to know what it is that you have us build.",
